name: Nena Trampa N.10
description:
Welcome summer on this side of the hemisphere!
Let's go to the beach girls or if you want I'll invite you to my pool.
The year is ending, I know it was hard, but summer has just begun.
The Kaleb already said it... 
"I know he hurt you
That he broke your heart
But today is not for crying
Today is pure fun"

Ese culo mami es uno en un millon, HACE CALOR!
